    "Finally, two application domains are pursued in this paper: (1) the pedagogical strategies commonly used in science courses, which were employed by Lai and Hwang (2015) and which include constructive, reflective, didactic, and unplugged pedagogies (Cope & Kalantzis, 2016), and (2) the learning tools, namely, hardware, software, intelligent agents, and unplugged strategies, which are coded as suggested by Ng and Chu (2021).",
